# Node (desktop-app, mobile-app)
node_modules/
dist/
*.exe
# These need the **/ prefix, not just a trailing slash — a bare
# "android/app/build/" is anchored to the repo root (a slash in the
# middle of a gitignore pattern anchors it) and silently misses
# mobile-app/android/app/build/, letting Gradle/CMake caches slip in.
**/android/build/
**/android/app/build/
**/android/.gradle/
**/android/app/.cxx/
**/ios/build/
**/ios/Pods/

# Unexplained directory that has appeared inside mobile-app/ during
# development — looks like some background tool on this machine mirroring
# build artifacts, not anything this project created. Never intentionally
# add; see CLAUDE.md's Windows Android build notes for context.
mobile-app/Explorer/
